  <summary date="2021-04-06T15:59:33Z" status="Introduced in House">Promoting Women in Trucking Workforce Act

This bill directs the Federal Motor Carrier Safety Administration to establish and facilitate a Women of Trucking Advisory Board to promote organizations and programs that (1) provide education, training, mentorship, or outreach to women in the trucking industry; and (2) recruit, retain, or advance women into the trucking industry.</summary>
